[section#syncstream.syncbuf.virtuals
    [:en] Overridden virtual functions
    [:zh_CN] 覆盖的虚函数
]

[%@lib@member sync[!basic_syncbuf]]
[codeblock:declaration]
int sync() override;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Records that the wrapped stream buffer is to be flushed.
[:zh_CN] 记录所包装的流缓冲区将被冲洗。

[:en] Then, if [*emit-on-sync] is [`true], calls [`emit()].
[:zh_CN] 然后，如果 [*emit-on-sync] 为 [`true]，则调用 [`emit()]。

[begin:note]
[:en] If [*emit-on-sync] is [`false], the actual flush is delayed until a call
to [`emit()].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [*emit-on-sync] 为 [`false]，则实际的冲洗将延迟到对 [`emit()] 的调用。
[end:note]

[para:returns]
[:en] If [`emit()] was called and returned [`false], returns [`-1]; otherwise [`0].
[:zh_CN] 如果调用了 [`emit()] 且其返回 [`false]，则返回 [`-1]；否则返回 [`0]。
[div:end]
